{"tid":231026,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[推理登] 一齊入黎討論下你睇過既推理作品／小說／漫畫／作家～","createTime":"2017-05-05T17:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T16:45:05.000Z","uid":30847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f668d376b223addfb255bbe9303c691a854c92fa","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家想討論咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作品類型不限，內容都無所謂，你睇完想分享下，又或者想討論下自己睇過既作品入面最好／最爛既詭計都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋下磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己就睇得唔算多，口味偏向本格作品，細個係睇呀媽既三色貓開始睇推理小說，西方作品就只係睇過圖書館借既福爾摩斯同羅蘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排睇完島田莊司既《星籠之海》，我自己就唔太鍾意個寫法。我比較鍾意佢前期作品，最鍾意《占星術殺人事件》同《奇想天慟》，《俄羅斯幽靈軍艦之謎》同《開膛手傑克的百年孤寂》都唔差<br />\n我硬係覺得佢D長篇作品九成九有伏，兩篇龍卧亭/水晶金字塔，呢類書至少有半本都寫左唔關事、可以刪走既文。同埋我覺得佢後期技窮，作品一係無詭計，一係D詭計穿鑿附會，一係就同你講純巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除此之外漫畫都有追，柯南就算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 金田一就偶有佳作劣作，偵探學園Q推理水準應該係三者中平均最高，不過我自己最鍾意睇金田一，幾鍾意入面既角色<br />\n<br />\n動畫都有睇過綾辻行人改篇既《Another》，初頭以為係推理作品，點知去到後期劇情暴走變做大逃殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b861db71c0fd97add8ab56d9fd1c713e5d83de3","tid":231026,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/015632_73d33b2b4782574be56b4ea10d3b8799.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F015632_73d33b2b4782574be56b4ea10d3b8799.png&h=91a2fc32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf33c0f4f93fd3f083441f847543a1096894678a","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/015632_73d33b2b4782574be56b4ea10d3b8799.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F015632_73d33b2b4782574be56b4ea10d3b8799.png&h=91a2fc32&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274dc2842f95000f25e921de97d7a1f7d898c16b","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae4af21fe46807fd7a889baee02ca529aa121a","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登有無人都係推理小說同好"},{"pid":"83d57a5de0948c33513c2c34a98f22caa4bd0f4a","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b06b375bb0bd52d38bf25071c0d4a4b37c1385","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":