09:03.000Z","msg":"出面炒車班人一個二個都話自己睇開推理小說偵探小說, 但係就無一個人入黎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a11d837b712f63984d773448b880280f55ad21c","tid":231026,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>龍騎士07算唔算<br />\n同埋睇過放學後推理(正傳反而冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n我只係睇過寒蟬, 無睇過龍騎士其他作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒蟬如果你係唔知頭唔知路去玩原作, 係唔錯<br />\n同埋海貓(建議睇漫畫)<br />\n不過呢類非本格推理有時係會睇到燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cf5958286bd09f7165030637ddc241d6b2e07a","tid":231026,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍騎士07算唔算<br />\n同埋睇過放學後推理(正傳反而冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n我只係睇過寒蟬, 無睇過龍騎士其他作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒蟬如果你係唔知頭唔知路去玩原作, 係唔錯<br />\n同埋海貓(建議睇漫畫)<br />\n不過呢類非本格推理有時係會睇到燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過太王道我又唔睇<br />\n次次都死人然後估兇手動機手法, 好侷限<br />\n推理應該係自由開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60848bca5c01dbb1bcc6c503810132937e20b45a","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍騎士07算唔算<br />\n同埋睇過放學後推理(正傳反而冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n我只係睇過寒蟬, 無睇過龍騎士其他作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒蟬如果你係唔知頭唔知路去玩原作, 係唔錯<br />\n同埋海貓(建議睇漫畫)<br />\n不過呢類非本格推理有時係會睇到燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海貓追緊漫畫，暫時追到ep6 (好多集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n我當係當初追寒蟬咁，希望最後episode 會解開返一切謎題<br />\n<br />\n其實個故事係咪由ep1開始，主角同家族係島上發生殺人事件<br />\n最後完結時主角唔願意相信魔女殺人說，所以開始左雙方既推理對決？(人類犯罪vs魔女犯罪說)<br />\n但我覺得有少少矛盾，忽略犯罪手法，理論上只有魔法存在，先會開始到推理棋局對決，主角想否認呢點我有少少睇唔明<br />\n同埋如果後面有解釋就唔好劇透我住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問真理亞佢係咪魔女既創始人？綠壽睇佢本日記係真實定妄想？"},{"pid":"7e1f29c9abe0591a904ff17674f7b50e930a895a","tid":231026,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍騎士07算唔算<br />\n同埋睇過放學後推理(正傳反而冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n我只係睇過寒蟬, 無睇過龍騎士其他作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒蟬如果你係唔知頭唔知路去玩原作, 係唔錯<br />\n同埋海貓(建議睇漫畫)<br />\n不過呢類非本格推理有時係會睇到燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過太王道我又唔睇<br />\n次次都死人然後估兇手動機手法, 好侷限<br />\n推理應該係自由開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我幾enjoy呢種寫法，我覺得佢以不可能犯罪=魔女殺人說 呢點幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋D角色都寫得幾好，我幾鍾意主角個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己鍾意，enjoy就得，我就無話分得好清本格作品/社會作品/其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過提起本格作品，我除左推理漫畫之外好少睇變形公館型既推理作品，因為單睇小說文字描寫理解唔到建築物既設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我都唔太鍾意島田莊司既本格寫法，夾硬加插一大段同推理/劇情無關，純粹充字數既獵奇段落描寫落作品度，不倫不類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19bdab78bfb9590adc77bc3fd159de539dd0f06","tid":231026,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍騎士07算唔算<br />\n同埋睇過放學後推理(正傳反而冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n我只係睇過寒蟬, 無睇過龍騎士其他作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒蟬如果你係唔知頭唔知路去玩原作, 係唔錯<br />\n同埋海貓(建議睇漫畫)<br />\n不過呢類非本格推理有時係會睇到燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海貓追緊漫畫，暫時追到ep6 (好多集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n我當係當初追寒蟬咁，希望最後episode 會解開返一切謎題<br />\n<br />\n其實個故事係咪由ep1開始，主角同家族係島上發生殺人事件<br />\n最後完結時主角唔願意相信魔女殺人說，所以開始左雙方既推理對決？(人類犯罪vs魔女犯罪說)<br />\n但我覺得有少少矛盾，忽略犯罪手法，理論上只有魔法存在，先會開始到推理棋局對決，主角想否認呢點我有少少睇唔明<br />\n同埋如果後面有解釋就唔好劇透我住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問真理亞佢係咪魔女既創始人？綠壽睇佢本日記係真實定妄想？</blockquote><br />\nMaria 唔係魔女既創始人"},{"pid":"66ceaaeb3667691e778827122dccbfa871549669","tid":231026,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T19:44:09.000Z","msg":"綾辻行人既館系列都相當唔錯"},{"pid":"822ba311e75dfb271e1fcb512de1bb4781209ab9","tid":231026,"uid":64559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"85980e6bb8e3ef431c18f13ffc0f9807ff2113de","tid":231026,"uid":2197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"伊阪幸太郎好過癮<br />\n有種單純的熱血"},{"pid":"6cc132d86acaea87ed246b53bc303aa75a456680","tid":231026,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike